ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 2 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2012-3 (Nekaneet)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 2 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT, NO. 2012-3 (NEKANEET) in order to add the name of the Province of Saskatchewan, the name of Nekaneet, an Indian band situated in Saskatchewan, the name of the band's council and the description of the reserves where the provincial-type tax could apply.
